  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>The primary objective of this analysis was to assess the difference in disease-free survival between post-menopausal women with hormone receptor-positive early breast cancer who switched from tamoxifen to anastrozole and those who continued on tamoxifen</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Assess the difference in overall survival/disease recurrence/safety and tolerability between post-menopausal women with hormone receptor-positive early breast cancer who switched from tamoxifen to anastrozole and those who continued to receive tamoxifen.</measure>
  </secondary_outcome>
